## Tech Stack
| Technology       | Purpose |
|------------------|--------|
| **Bolt.new**     | AI-powered initial project generation |
| **React + TypeScript** | Frontend framework |
| **Vite**         | Build tool & development server |
| **Tailwind CSS** | Responsive, modern styling |
| **Netlify**      | Static hosting & global CDN |

---

## Project Features
- Clean, Kenya-themed UI with flag and safari-inspired design
- Fully responsive (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Interactive visa application form
- Simulated processing steps
- Fast loading (Vite-optimized)
- Production-ready static build

---

## How to Run Locally

### 1. Development Mode
```bash
git clone https://github.com/gaiuscodes/VisaVibeKe.git
cd VisaVibeKe
npm install
npm run dev
